descriptionHtml:

http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/814239-two-quick-meshes-onions-and-fiddleheads/

Fiddlehead and onion mesh (nif) + textures (dds) for your mods, atm they work as green/red apple replacer (for preview), you have to adjust the nif/texture and add it to your mod / make them standalone yourself. Pls don't download if you don't know how to handle the files.
